{"tid":317343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國政府全面禁止個人VPN的使用","createTime":"2017-07-11T11:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T11:30:26.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd14ab440967eb27cce60a2261291e719c347a7d","tid":317343,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"為進一步加強對資訊的監管及操控，有消息指中國政府將會在明年2月以前，全面禁止使用個人 VPN，更要求電訊商戶包括中國移動、中國電信、中國聯通，全面配合有關係政策，意味著內地網民不能再透過「翻牆」手段，來接觸一些被大陸屏蔽的網頁、服務了。根據彭博通訊社的報導，有關的禁令不單是針對個人 VPN ，更包括 VPN 等網路代理技術，像 Shadowsocks 之類別的 VPN 代理服務也要在中國網絡上全面絕跡。 <br />\n<br />\n資料來源 : Bloomberg <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/07/11/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5&d=%2BorDB%2BNLk3YiV8Fdp8gYIJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4bc5a13f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/07/11/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5</a>"},{"pid":"5017af0604b48d2a26278c6155051311f06766cd","tid":317343,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4b5b1833b97548270d8b0a84af15ab8798ff4","tid":317343,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:27:51.000Z","msg":"支持 中國人係需要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598c76c9cf9c2fcb1e2691744a8f49c085d905a5","tid":317343,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:28:30.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd59426dbba1c6fb2482ec584216eef1ab0ea534","tid":317343,"uid":50740,"li